And we have looked at many different aspects and things, but today specifically, we are gonna look at, I will lead my family to be a healthy church member.

01:48.445 --> 01:56.294
There are a story of three pastors that had gathered for coffee and shared their bat infestation problem.

01:56.574 --> 02:03.602
